"SELECT" statement is use to select data from a database. 

SYNTAX:
a.
SELECT * FROM table_name;  
* --> represent all, which means it selects all the columns of a table. 

b. 
SELECT column_name_1, column_name_2, ... 
FROM table_name; 
It selects only the specifiec column of a table. 

C. SELECT DISTINCT column_name FROM table_name; 
DISTINCT statement select non-repeated(distinct) columns from the given table.
